  <description>
    <p>
      WineZGUI (pronounced Wine-Zee-Goo-Eee) is a wine frontend for playing windows games with wine easily. It is a collection of Bash scripts for Wine Prefix Management and Linux Desktop Integration for easier wine gaming experience using Zenity.
    </p>
    <p>WineZGUI features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Runs windows games or exe files from file manager.</li>
      <li>Creates application shortcut for easier access.</li>
      <li>Separate prefix for every exe file launched with WineZGUI</li>
      <li>Imports other wine directory from Bottles, Wine, Lutris, Heroic Launcher into WineZGUI and create shortcuts for all found exes.</li>
      <li>Backup and Restore prefixes for later use.</li>
      <li>Runners (different builds of wine like proton) can be used with prefixes</li>
      <li>Create Game Bundles for sharing (prefix+game)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
